(secondQuint)Ocytocine and Cerebral Activation in Relation With Attachement.

 Healthy adult male will be recruited.

 Their attachement style will be assessed through the Attachement scale interview (ASI).

 They will have 2 fMRI sessions, during which emotional images will be presented.

 One session will be preceded by a nasal administration of oxytocin and the other session will be preceded by a placebo nasal administration.

 The order of both administrations will be randomized.

